    {
      "say": "Control M lands on the first non-blank. Indented lines start at the variable name, not the spaces."
    },
    {
      "wait": 0.3
    },
    {
      "comment": "--- Demo 3: why this matters ---"
    },
    {
      "say": "Why does this matter? Some people remap J to join lines or move text down. Control J still moves the cursor down. It is built into the terminal layer, not the mapping system.",
